divs: Sighting Detailswas heading to work on or about july 2002 on route 99 near the entrance to the NRV speedway, and i just happened to look up and about 1 o'clock high was a "aircraft" that was shaped roughly like a old child's top in battleship grey color. the next day on the same route i happened to look up and i saw a "aircraft" shaped like a warp nacell off a star trek NX class starship (cylindrical). a couple of days after the encounter i'd seen a squadron of blackhawks in this formation > , along with a unmarked bell 420? hovering in the trees near my house about 100'. the unmarked helo had no markings except a stripe coming down the engine cowl angled towards the cockpit.
